It's a simple matter that this world, and all in it, are tainted, evil, and impure. That's why you have entities like the Lust for Blood, or even the Knighthood of Mithaniel Marr. Both are filled with such hate! They seek to kill and destroy those who fit their definition &quot;evil&quot; without really seeing that their struggle is in vain and silly; everyone here is evil. Even I am filled with some &quot;hate,&quot; some desire to purge what is &quot;evil.&quot; I'm evil, you're evil, this tavern is evil. It's the birthright of having been born into this... prison. As I said, I don't hold myself above any others.<br>
