<br>
But I understand if this seems like hatred to you. If it makes you feel more secure in your bondage, you may see me as evil, a servitor of darkness and not the pure nihil. You will eventually glimpse the truth, though. Your eyes will open and you will feel free as a sword thrusts through you and drains the life from your body -- at least until the curse of this world drags you back, kicking and screaming. <br>
<br>
In the end, the warm embrace of death is all I seek to offer, to free us all from our cage.<br>
