<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>The barmaid returns, bearing a glass of port. The woman sips it gingerly, then continues.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> Fear not, though, loves. There are many more who yearn for the nihil, who desire my love, and they will be freed from this mortal coil first. The quest is so large, I can wait for you to understand.<br>
